::Kup::

Kup got into the CR chamber, and had his alt mode refited for the energon.
Kup then went to the mess hall, to help Talos with the clean up. Kup started to pick up and repair the shelves.

::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod quickly put some space between him and Grimlock.

&quot;Hold on there, old buddy. I didn&#39;t crash the ship this time, I swear on the Matrix. I wasn&#39;t even on the bridge.&quot;

Hot Rod remembered how he used to crash ships quite often. He especialy remembered when him, Kup, Grimlock, and the rest of the Dinobots had crashed on Quintessa, and had nearly been fed to Sharkticons by the Quintesons.

&quot;I knew you were on board, and I just came to make sure you were ok. Nice way to treat a former commanding officer, Grimlock.&quot;


